<div class="modal fade" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" id="miner-modal">
<div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
<div class="modal-content">
<div class="modal-header">
<button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
</div>
<div class="modal-body">
<div class="monero">
<img src="/assets/img/monero-logo.png" />
</div>
<p class="info">
We are now offering a way to securely support the costs of MangaStream <strong>and</strong> browse
without ads for free. In exchange, we will use a portion of your computer's processing power in the background
while you read manga to calculate hashes for Monero (a cryptocurrency like Bitcoin). Please
carefully read the notes below to understand what this is.
</p>
<ol>
<li>While calculating hashes (mining), we won't use 100% of your CPU.</li>
<li>If you use a third party anti-virus program, it may falsely flag the opt-in as malicious code. This is because of all the sites out there that will run these Crypto miners without your consent - we are being fully transparent and cooperative.</li>
<li>This isn't dangerous to your hardware in most cases, but please ensure your desktop is properly ventilated if you run it for long periods of time as your cores will run hotter than normal use.</li>
<li>You will be asked to opt-in every 24-hrs or so to ensure you're always aware when it's on, and consenting to it.</li>
<li>You can turn it off at any time, the button to toggle it will appear in the header while the miner is running.</li>
<li>Mining can only happen while you're on MangaStream, when you leave the site your CPU resources will immediately be freed up.</li>
</ol>
<p class="info">
If you'd like to get started, click the button below. You will be prompted with an additional
opt-in agreement with the vendor (CoinHive) on behalf of our site (readms.net). You can close this
box if you don't want to participate.
</p>
<a href="javascript:;" id="miner-optin" class="btn btn-primary">Continue (Opt-In Dialog)</a>
</div>
